## ğŸ“± Eyebrow Tracker App

The **Eyebrow Tracker** module prompts the user to raise their eyebrows and uses Appleâ€™s **Vision Framework** to detect motion in the left and right eyebrows relative to the eyes.

### Features:
- On-device face landmark detection (VNDetectFaceLandmarksRequest)
- Calculates vertical eyebrow-eye distance delta
- Displays: â€œLeft raisedâ€, â€œRight raisedâ€, â€œBoth evenâ€, or â€œNo movementâ€
- Runs offline with no cloud dependency

### Demo:
![eyebrow demo](screenshots/eyebrow-demo.gif)

