## ğŸ§  Clinical Relevance

Neurocognition tools are inspired by clinical needs in neurology, geriatrics, and emergency care â€” especially for rapid stroke screening, early detection of cognitive decline, and fall risk. This project evolved from real-world work with physicians at **Mayo Clinic** and continues through **Sonoran Robotics LLC** in partnership with the **University of Arizona Center for Innovation**.

